quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  52,1,S udrar
  52,2,S Tezmamt ippujerrden
  52,3,di lka$ev ivelqen
  52,4,S texxamt iâamôen
  52,5,S tseddarit aâlayen
  52,6,S yill icebbwlen
  52,7,"Aâaqeb n Mass ik, s tidep, ad ivôu"
  52,8,Ur isâi ara t sfunngen
  52,9,"Ass ideg ara imbwiwel igenni, d ambwiwel"
  52,10,"Ad lêun idurar, d tikli"
  52,11,"A ssexv, assen, n wid iskiddiben"
  52,12,Wid inexôen deg uraren
  52,13,"Ass ideg ara pwaveggôen ar tmes n Loahennama, d aveggeô"
  52,14,Apan tmes nni i la tnekôem
  52,15,"D ssêur waya, ne$ d kunwi ur nwala ara"
  52,16,"Kecmet ep. Iâuva fellawen, tûebôem, ne$ ur teûbiôem. A ppeppuqeîîim kan $ef wayen txeddmem"
  52,17,"Wanag wid ipêezziben, di leonanat, akked zzhu"
  52,18,"Feôêen s wayen i sen Ifka Mass nnsen. Isellek iten, Mass nnsen, seg uâaqeb ujajiê"
  52,19,"àçet, teswem, di lehna, ilmend n wayen txeddmem"
  52,20,"èélen af imîeôêen, d idurra; d tiêuôiyin lâin ukud iten Njewweo"
  52,21,"Wid iumnen, u âanden ten, warraw nnsen, ar liman nnsen, a ten Nessemlil akked warraw nnsen. Ur Nessenqas acemma seg igiten nnsen. Yal amdan ad immager ayen ikseb"
  52,22,Ad asen d Nefk izwayen akked uksum seg wayen cedhan
  52,23,"Dinna ad ppemyeppaken lkas, ideg ur illi usîeômel, ne$ ssebba n tuccva"
  52,24,"Garasen, ddewiôen ilmeéiyen i nitni, amzun d tiyaqutin mesîuôen"
  52,25,"Zzin, kra $er kra, pmesteqsayen"
  52,26,"Nnan d: \"ni$ nella, zik, di twacult nne$, nugad"
  52,27,"I$at a$ Öebbi, Isellek a$ seg ujajiê n tmes"
  52,28,"Ni$ nella, zik, nepnuju $uôeS. Neppa, s tidep, d A$eyyat Ipêunun"